model_overview.name: model_overview
model_overview.value: This reservoir serves the water supply needs of Harrisonburg.  There are no intakes in the reservoir, rather, flows that leave the reservoir are picked up downstream in the Dry River. Outflows are a function of storage level in the reservoir and are not currently governed by any permitted minimum release, but rather, by natural variations in head at different water levels.
